Company Description: Founded IN 1948, Mcdonald's Is One Of The Leading Food Service Retailers IN The World. Located At New York, N.Y., It Operates More Than 32,000 Locations IN 117 Countries Serving Around 60 Million Customers Daily. The Restaurant Chain Offers Various Food Items, Including Big Mac, Quarter Pounder, Chicken Mcnuggets And Egg Mcmuffin Along With A Variety Of Beverages. The Chain Also Offers Meal Bundles, Including Dollar Menu, Extra Value Meals, Happy Meals And Mighty Kids Meals For Family And Children. Mcdonald's Also Offers Special Dishes From Various Countries Of The World, Including Brazil, Hong Kong, Italy And Portugal, To Name A Few. It Features IN Fortune Magazine's List Of Most Admired Company IN The World As Well As IN Barron's Magazine's 2010 Annual Survey As Most Respected Company. The Company Also Offers Free WI-Fi, Arch Card, Play Places And Party Services.

Mcdonald S Is A Global Food Service Retailer That Operates More Than 30,000 Locations IN Over 100 Countries. The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Fish, Salads, Fruit And Sandwiches. It Additionally Offers French Fries, Chicken Sandwiches, Quarter Pounders And Honey Wheat Rolls. The Restaurant S Menu Also Includes The Ranch Snack Wrap, Big N' Tasty, Chicken Selects And Mcflurry Treats. It Serves A Variety Of Beverages And Desserts, Including Chocolate Triple Thick, Minty Mudd Bath Triple Thick And Strawberry Triple Thick Shakes And Mcdonaldland Cookies. Mcdonald's Restaurants Are Owned And Operated By Independent Franchisees Of The Mcdonald's Corporation.
